{"tid":657984,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"未放抵ex 但選擇開始新戀情","createTime":"2018-05-08T14:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T18:05:36.000Z","uid":134054,"like":28,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cbdef99fa0f713e1ce9ea68b784dd993fb4ff485","tid":657984,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:19:55.000Z","msg":"你地有無後悔過傷害多個人? <br />\n未搞掂自己 諗住試下新戀情<br />\n以為靠新對象可以move on快D?<br />\n最後只會比較 心痛 無左拍拖既意義<br />\n過多幾年先發覺放唔抵 現任hurt爆<br />\n<br />\n咁點解唔面對自己內心搵返ex重頭來過? <br />\n好好珍惜時間 一過咗就真係無<br />\n世界雖然大 但係你估唔到聽日發生咩事<br />\n如果ex有咩不幸 真係一世嫁啦<br />\n抱住過得一日得一日既心態 開開心心同愛既人一齊先不枉此生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n除左被帽賤人ex外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78701b288c0bab8fea3fb05422d3401a90373f0d","tid":657984,"uid":828,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:24:19.000Z","msg":"有嘢唔啱先會變ex 唔好害人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53053b97ccf3a4a28c80a15d58f0f775d0a38f1f","tid":657984,"uid":27793,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T14:58:12.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n未放低ex 而且佢ex無可能接受返佢嗰啲<br />\n<br />\n一日未放低 一日都咪害人<br />\n孤獨終老都咪害新人"},{"pid":"dac9972d559b05f49499541e8b638c574fc72f72","tid":657984,"uid":122115,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T15:00:16.000Z","msg":"最慘既係做撚左人水泡都唔知<br />\n<br />\n呢一年都唔自己on99係到做乜春<br />\n<br />\n好想快啲忘記佢"},{"pid":"d9ddb4ef8cc3dceebee9732417ba1c0f9892088b","tid":657984,"uid":36389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T18:09:44.000Z","msg":"唉......人好犯賤"},{"pid":"f253e14cf8bd49b8d6e0a7ac6cc23490fc156c3d","tid":657984,"uid":183030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T18:39:14.000Z","msg":"see....<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets